        "content": "<p>sorry, I'm not sure whether I understood it correctly, but <code>IsOrderBornology</code> inherits to subtypes? <code>Real</code> has it but <code>Ioo 0 1</code> does not, I guess (<code>univ</code> is bounded in <code>Ioo 0 1</code> but does not have upper/lower bound in it...)</p>",
